QuestData.Title: Ashenvale Outrunners
QuestData.Description: Blasted elves! Dey knew right where to hit us!$b$bIt was dem outrunners... I tried to warn 'em that we were being spied on, but no one listened. Now look at us - cooped up here like chickens!$b$bNever too late for vengeance, mon! Hunt 'em down and make 'em pay for what they done!
QuestData.RewardText: Good, good!$b$bThe fewer 'a dem elves runnin' around, the better.
